      "rationale": "CFD NIH predictions compared against bench measurements at five operating points. Mean absolute error 8.3%; all predictions within ±15% of measured values. Systematic over-prediction of 6–9% at high flow rates noted and attributed to turbulence model limitations at Re > 8000; documented as coverage gap but within acceptable tolerance for MRL 2.",
