      "rationale": "Formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2. The k-ω SST turbulence model selection is justified by published benchmark comparisons for rotating blood pump geometries (Fraser et al. 2011; Hariharan et al. 2018). Giersiepen hemolysis power-law model is the FDA-recognized approach for this device class. Model form adequacy is implicitly assessed through the output comparison factor."
