      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Sample-to-sample geometric variability assessment is not required at MRL 2. A single pump specimen machined to nominal tolerances was used for bench validation; dimensional inspection report confirms all features within ±0.05 mm of nominal CAD geometry. Manufacturing variability effects are addressed through the geometric sensitivity study in the broader design analysis."
